{"title":"个人博客建站指南","date":"2019-03-16T21:06:08.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Mar 16, 2019","L":"03/16/2019","MM-DD":"03-16"},"link":"2019/03/16/个人博客建站指南","tags":["博客"],"categories":["Hexo"],"updated":"2023-03-21T13:39:40.258Z","content":"<h1 id=\"个人博客建站指南\">个人博客建站指南<a title=\"#个人博客建站指南\" href=\"#个人博客建站指南\"></a></h1>\n<p>必要条件</p>\n<ol>\n<li>安装 Git</li>\n<li>安装 Nodejs</li>\n<li>GitHub</li>\n</ol>\n<p>步骤</p>\n<p>安装</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>需要本地运行时安装</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-server --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>初始化</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo init &lt;your blog stored folder&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>本地运行</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>默认浏览URL：<code>127.0.0.1:4000</code></p>\n<p>部署</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo deploy </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"参考\">参考<a title=\"#参考\" href=\"#参考\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/\" target=\"_blank\">Hexo 中文文档</a></li>\n<li></li>\n</ul>\n","prev":{"title":"Java 异常机制","link":"2022/09/20/exceptions"},"plink":"https://hadron404.github.io/blog/2019/03/16/个人博客建站指南/","toc":[{"id":"个人博客建站指南","title":"个人博客建站指南","index":"1","children":[{"id":"参考","title":"参考","index":"1.1"}]}],"reading_time":"85 words in 1 min"}